{"tid":1386370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉］一班社工淨係罷工無撚用架！","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T01:59:59.000Z","uid":172979,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"379f1d486d1318c63aec02a39faad8e521da5c3e","tid":1386370,"uid":172979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:28:43.000Z","msg":"標題黨引左巴絲入黎 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除左罷工，仲要社福界罷埋市</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家都知社福界發起8月5日發夢時大罷工 <br />\n但係一班社工擁抱大愛精神，怕得失社會福利署。驚服務單位有懲野有處分。一切都係bullshit.<br />\n知道好多社界同工巴絲都為左唔好影響服務原則之下發起罷工/用最低人手維持服務！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實係無撚用！！！！<br />\n其實係無撚用！！！！<br />\n其實係無撚用！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n對於社署對於政權黎講，一班社工罷工唔罷市根本毫無影響力。<br />\n如果要帶來影響力，一定要罷埋市, close埋center啦（高危緊急服務單位除外）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">罷市先係實踐癱瘓香港的唯一真理！！！<br />\n罷市先係實踐癱瘓香港的唯一真理！！！<br />\n罷市先係實踐癱瘓香港的唯一真理！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n咁多位社福同工巴絲，只要我地多團體多NGO咁做，社署一定唔敢秋後算帳！<br />\n難聽d講,如果驚SQS追究，之後先再算啦。Sick leave 都唔係前線同工責任。<br />\n最多之後咪開多一日比社署。 <br />\n<br />\n除非個service unit 好撚高危/urgent service  <br />\nEg. 任何緊急宿舍、院舍、IFSC、ICCMW等等<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句，如果係普通DECC、NEC、 ICYFC、CC、NLCDP、URSST、甚至社企等的服務<br />\n無社工唔會死既service，反而香港死左，仲難救。 <br />\n罷撚埋市啦屌！ <br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示： <br />\n社福界同工唔好再執著罷工需唔需要拎假定NO pay leave. <br />\n*要對準罷工最撚大既效果係癱瘓社會，表達五大訴求*<br />\n非工業行動既罷工無人工，絕對好撚合理。 <br />\n<br />\n咁多位同工 <br />\n如果您睇到呢個post, 呼籲埋隔離位同事，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">集體Sick leave, 實行罷市癱瘓香港！！<br />\n集體Sick leave, 實行罷市癱瘓香港！！<br />\n集體Sick leave, 實行罷市癱瘓香港！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n1. 立即撤回「逃犯條例修訂」。<br />\n2. 收回「612暴動」定性。<br />\n3. 成立獨立調查委員會，以調查警方於整場反送中運動過份濫用暴力執法。<br />\n4. 律政司必須保持政治中立，絕不可政治檢控。<br />\n5. 落實雙普選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HU8Eab6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHU8Eab6.png&h=f44eb8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPvnSqs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPvnSqs.png&h=f0fa77b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpRm7YO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpRm7YO.png&h=45ec081d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L5A7i5u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL5A7i5u.png&h=5e4a14f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1D6VsYQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1D6VsYQ.png&h=52d25c54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bvev1iQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbvev1iQ.png&h=179afa12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4QrzDQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4QrzDQ.png&h=83e4e4b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oW2Sqw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oW2Sqw.png&h=b2a4da25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XRCdY5x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXRCdY5x.png&h=ac45c9d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4eacca732015c66e08a4c36adddbe65828431c58","tid":1386370,"uid":172979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:32:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a8f7e4945d041fe8ac73c3ca2d29bda6907c57f","tid":1386370,"uid":172979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:32:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f59ac1340fa7dd8e5f65add29dbfcc785a86a2c4","tid":1386370,"uid":282505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13705ef49973d3a2bd33abfe614b2fb88cf0a6b9","tid":1386370,"uid":14714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"又得啫"},{"pid":"7a0b71ee2152331f4539ff8a82c94e8c13e5fbfb","tid":13863